response.original_title: Chet Atkins: A Life in Music
response.overview: A documentary that celebrates the life and career of musician and record executive Chet Atkins with guest stars including Dolly Parton, Mark Knopfler, George Benson, Steve Howe, Vince Gill, Randy Bachman, Les Paul, Waylon Jennings and Willie Nelson.
response.tagline: Celebrating the life and career of Chet Atkins
response.title: Chet Atkins: A Life in Music
